{
  "texts": [
    "This process involves understanding that microwaves can heat water, that ground coffee needs to be mixed with hot water to extract flavor, and that the mixture needs time to steep the coffee.",
    "For this instruction, the model needed to understand that microwaves can be used to heat liquids -information it extracted from its training data.",
    "It also needed to know that coffee is usually created by the interaction of hot water and ground beans, and that extraction takes time.",
    "This means that the model had to represent concepts of heat application, liquid extraction and timing in order to generate such an instruction.",
    "This is done even though such specific instructions for making coffee in a microwave may not have been exactly present in the training data."
  ]
}